image.title: Flora Clark and Kurt.
image.comments: Me as a baby and Aunt Flora. I have fond memories of Aunt Flora and I taking Kleenex tissue, wetting it, rolling it into a ball then wrapping it with rubber bands after it dried for the sole purpose of chucking the things at each other in a game of hide and seek upstairs at Grandpa and Grandma Wilson's house. I don't know how we came up with it but it was great fun. -Kurt
